<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, December 9 (Xinhua) -- A senior European Union (EU)
official said today that Zambia is on the right track in
support should be expected, Zambia News Agency ZANA reported.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a luncheon hosted for the visiting EU officials at
Panodzi Hotel here, Jose'da Silva Domingos, EU director for
eastern and southern Africa, hailed the Zambian government for
