Army Lions 88-56, Jiangsu Nangang trounced Beijing Shougang 82-68,
Guangdong Hongyuan ousted Jinan Army Pegasus 95-79 and Liaoning
Hunters beat home team Zhejiang Zhongxin 75-69.
