to condemn the Iraqi decision, calling it an "unjust" one.
</P>
<P>
The Jordanian-Iraqi relations suffered a setback after the 1991
Gulf War. But the relations have been picking up as Iraq is
increasing oil sale to and imports from Jordan. 
