development in some Asian countries were as a result effective
management and leadership which, Diya said, was worthy of
emulation by Nigeria.
</P>
<P>
He urged Nigerian engineers to require a level of managerial
capacity or competence to turn the nation into a great country,
taking advantage of its enormous natural and material resources.
