<HEADLINE> Chinese Women Lifter Sets World Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHIANG MAI, December 10 (Xinhua) -- Chen Yanqing of China set a
new world record in the jerk of the women's 64kg division at the
World Weightlifting Championships here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Chen jerked 131 kilograms, beating the listed mark of 130.5kg
set by her compatriot Shi Lihua in August. 
</P>
