<HEADLINE> Shanghai Expects to Be China's Major Compressor Producer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, December 10 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai is expected to become
China's major compressor producer and exporter with the recent
startup of a Sino-U.S. joint-venture.
</P>
<P>
